## Bare Metal

Add user to `www-data` group:

```bash
sudo usermod -a -G www-data anne
```

Create `/var/www/html/public-html/`

## Vue

```bash
pnpm create vue@latest

Project name: desky
Add TypeScript?: Y
Add JSX Support?: Y
Add Vue Router for SPA dev? Y
Add Pinia for state mgmt? Y
Add Vitest for Unit Testing?Y
Add an End-to-End Testin Solution? No
ESLint? Y
Vue DevTools? Y

Scaffolding project in /home/anne/prod/desky...

Done. Now run:

  cd desky
  pnpm install
  pnpm dev
```

Configure External Port

Add to `vite.config.ts`:

```typescript
 export default defineConfig({
  // ...some configs
  server: {
    port: 3000,
  },
});
```

or edit `package.json`:

```json
 "dev": "vite --host ip --port 3000",
```

Open port in firewall:

```bash
sudo ufw allow 3000/tcp
```

Open Fordwarding Port to local router

Add DNS A rec


